==Useful Info==
'''Deathcaps''' are essentially an undead form of [[wandering mushroom]]. They can drain life from you and your allies from anywhere within its [[LOS]]. They do not occur naturally, and can only be encountered if summoned by a [[curse toe]]'s [[Summon Mushrooms]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*The main threat of deathcaps is the curse toe itself, who'll [[torment]] you. A deathcap's attacks can finish off players who've been tormented to low HP. The amount of mushrooms can make it hard to move, and their [[confusion]]-branded melee can make it harder to fight the toe.

==History==
*Deathcaps were added in [[0.13]].
